title: Eiffel I'm in Love
actors: Shandy Aulia, Samuel Rizal, Vena Annisa, Yogi Finanda, Arifin Hilda, Titi Kamal, Tommy Kurniawan, Didi Petet
description: A teenage girl, Tita, who led a perfect life. Her life completely changes when her parents good friend and his son, Adit, came from France to stay with them.
